file.name: openapi.yaml
file.content:
security:
  - jwtBearer: []
info:
  title: HPI Schul-Cloud Analytics Service API
  description:
    This is the API specification for the HPI Schul-Cloud Analytics service.
    
  contact:
    name: support
    email: info@dbildungscloud.de
  license:
    name: GPL-3.0
    url: 'https://github.com/hpi-schul-cloud/schulcloud-server/blob/master/LICENSE'
  version: 1.0.0
components:
  securitySchemes:
    jwtBearer:
      type: http
      scheme: bearer
      bearerFormat: JWT
  schemas:
    analytics:
      description: TODO
paths:
  /analytics:
    post:
      parameters: []
      responses:
        '201':
          description: created
          content:
            application/json:
              schema:
                $ref: '#/components/schemas/analytics'
        '401':
          description: not authenticated
        '500':
          description: general error
      description: Creates a new resource with data.
      summary: ''
      tags:
        - analytics
      security: []
      requestBody:
        required: true
        content:
          application/json:
            schema:
              $ref: '#/components/schemas/analytics'
openapi: 3.0.2
tags:
  - name: analytics
    description: An analytics service.
